'''啤酒救世界'''（{{lang-en|How beer saved the world}}）是[[探索頻道|探索頻道]]的一小时[[紀錄片|紀錄片]] ，播出于2011年11月30日<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.craftbeer.com/pages/news-and-events/news/show?title=discovery-channel-presents-how-beer-saved-the-world|title=News: Discovery Channel Presents "How Beer Saved the World"|accessdate=2012-09-18|publisher=CraftBeer.com|archive-date=2011-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110130113337/http://www.craftbeer.com/pages/news-and-events/news/show?title=discovery-channel-presents-how-beer-saved-the-world|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，由澳大利亚Beyond Productions制作，介绍了[[啤酒|啤酒]]的起源以及它如何影响如建造[[埃及金字塔|埃及金字塔]]和创造现代医学等人类历史上的重大事件。<ref name="GT 1/28/12">{{cite web|url=http://www.gazettetimes.com/news/local/article_14b20f18-2ac4-11e0-a7a7-001cc4c002e0.html|title=Beer documentary features OSU|accessdate=2012-09-18|date=2011-01-28|publisher=Gazettetimes.com|archive-date=2017-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171207140129/http://www.gazettetimes.com/news/local/article_14b20f18-2ac4-11e0-a7a7-001cc4c002e0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.the-standard.org/life/entertainment/how-beer-saved-the-world-brings-light-to-age-old/article_cea4b7e8-56b2-11e1-a1e9-001a4bcf6878.html|title=‘How Beer Saved the World’ brings light to age-old debate|accessdate=27 November 2014|last=Simpson|first=Nick|publisher=The Standard|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913235643/http://www.the-standard.org/life/entertainment/how-beer-saved-the-world-brings-light-to-age-old/article_cea4b7e8-56b2-11e1-a1e9-001a4bcf6878.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

